1
00:01:38,800 --> 00:01:39,360
Mr. Ye,

2
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,320
did Xiaoyun tell you?

3
00:01:42,039 --> 00:01:42,770
Tell me what?

4
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,860
About me borrowing money.

5
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:48,520
Mr. Ye,

6
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,520
please just lend me the money.

7
00:01:50,520 --> 00:01:52,250
I will definitely pay you back.

8
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,580
I can't help you with this.

9
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,530
Mr. Ye, I'm begging you.

10
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:59,020
I really have no other way.

11
00:01:59,120 --> 00:01:59,979
Please help me.

12
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:00,700
Let go of me.

13
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,320
Tian Liang.

14
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:09,780
You were the one who told me to follow him.

15
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,480
Now he is dead.

16
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:14,040
I'm going to tell the police.

17
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,800
You can't get away with this either.

18
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,660
What are you doing?

19
00:02:27,480 --> 00:02:28,010
Come out.

20
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,280
Come out here!

21
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:33,380
What are you doing?

22
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,480
You bastard.

23
00:02:34,880 --> 00:02:36,680
You lied to me time and time again,

24
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,740
and I put up with it.

25
00:02:38,079 --> 00:02:39,200
You spend my money,

26
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,360
living it up

27
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,440
and acting recklessly out there,

28
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:43,500
leaving a huge mess for me to clean up.

29
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:45,090
Do you have any bottom line?

30
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,490
You killed Tian Liang, didn't you?

31
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:49,840
Go,

32
00:02:50,040 --> 00:02:50,800
turn yourself in.

33
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,120
Go.

34
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,280
I didn't kill him. Let's go.

35
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:54,680
The police station is just ahead. Let's go.

36
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:55,600
Ye Qiming,

37
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,640
are you beating around the bush with me?

38
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:58,500
Let me tell you.

39
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,280
Those people in your photos,

40
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,920
I've investigated all of them.

41
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,120
If you leave me to die,

42
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,840
then we'll go down together.

43
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:07,080
I just don't understand.

44
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,720
You have so much money.

45
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:09,120
Why can't you lend me some?

46
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,980
It's not like I won't pay you back.

47
00:03:11,560 --> 00:03:13,200
Paying back the money is a small matter,

48
00:03:13,200 --> 00:03:15,930
but taking care of yourself is what's important.

49
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:18,730
The money you owe me,

50
00:03:19,440 --> 00:03:21,160
whether you pay it back or not isn't important.

51
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,280
A proper college student,

52
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:24,010
look at what you've become now.

53
00:03:25,760 --> 00:03:27,280
Whether you've done right by me,

54
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,360
we can skip that for now.

55
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:30,200
But have you done right by yourself?

56
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:31,440
Have you done right by your mother?

57
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:33,160
Don't you know how you've survived until today?

58
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:35,360
Your conscience has been eaten by dogs.

59
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:37,840
Mr. Ye.

60
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:38,960
Uncle Ye.

61
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,360
I'm sorry.

62
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:42,280
I was just talking nonsense.

63
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,280
Please save me.

64
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,560
I really have no way out.

65
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,480
The person in the surveillance video is Lu Yang.

66
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:51,520
He is a student at the University of Science and Technology.

67
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:52,850
On the night of the 25th,

68
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,170
he was at the bar.

69
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,840
It's a bit blurry.

70
00:03:56,760 --> 00:03:58,280
I feel like I've seen him before.

71
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,200
He is very likely

72
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:01,060
the last person to see Tian Liang.

73
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:02,400
Have you checked all the surveillance cameras

74
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,130
around here?

75
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,040
Yes, we have.

76
00:04:04,440 --> 00:04:05,200
The main thing is that the two of them

77
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:07,040
didn't appear in the surveillance cameras again.

78
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:08,100
Why not summon him?

79
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:11,480
The timeline doesn't match up, Captain Shen.

80
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:11,810
Look.

81
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,280
At 9:30 PM that night,

82
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:15,900
Lu Yang left the bar and followed Tian Liang.

83
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,160
At 10:00 PM, he appeared

84
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,519
in a nearby internet cafe.

85
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,480
I have checked with the person in charge

86
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,680
of the internet cafe.

87
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:22,320
He did arrive at 10:00 PM,

88
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:25,090
and it was caught on the surveillance camera.

89
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:27,840
Half an hour to kill and dismember someone

90
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:28,900
is not enough time.

91
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,800
Gather the police force

92
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:34,000
and search the area where Tian Liang disappeared.

93
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:37,060
Try to find the primary crime scene as soon as possible.

94
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:39,800
By the way.

95
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,400
Do we have a clearer picture

96
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,400
of this Lu Yang?

97
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,180
Master.

98
00:04:42,560 --> 00:04:44,420
I knew you would ask me about this.

99
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:46,100
I've already prepared it.

100
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:46,720
Look.

101
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:47,380
This...

102
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,440
is a clearer picture of Lu Yang.

103
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,360
No.

104
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:57,280
Li.

105
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,280
No.

106
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:00,200
He looks exactly the same, Zhao.

107
00:05:00,200 --> 00:05:00,600
Look.

108
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:01,860
They look so alike.

109
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,360
Li.

110
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:05,520
Here's what you do.

111
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:07,180
Go buy the same clothes as him,

112
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:09,400
stroll around his school tomorrow,

113
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:10,930
and say you're his brother.

114
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,080
Right.

115
00:05:12,360 --> 00:05:12,960
Good idea.

116
00:05:12,960 --> 00:05:13,480
Yes.

117
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:14,320
Don't say too much when people ask,

118
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,160
or you'll give yourself away.

119
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:16,960
You'll definitely find out something useful.

120
00:05:16,960 --> 00:05:17,680
No, this...

121
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,040
Is this reliable, Master?

122
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,700
No, Master.

123
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,490
Okay, stop messing around.

124
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,280
Stop messing around.

125
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,810
Let's get down to business.

126
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,760
I'll reimburse you for the clothes.

127
00:05:32,320 --> 00:05:33,159
Okay.

128
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:34,050
For the case.

129
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,200
Zhao.

130
00:05:41,440 --> 00:05:41,970
Let's go.

131
00:05:44,960 --> 00:05:45,800
Didn't Captain Jiang ask you to buy

132
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,130
the exact same clothes?

133
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,440
I really couldn't find them.

134
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,930
Zhao, do you think this one will do?

135
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,840
If you don't have it, there's nothing we can do.

136
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:55,170
Here.

137
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:55,760
Thanks.

138
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,010
I'm telling you,

139
00:05:58,480 --> 00:06:00,640
listening to Captain Shen is definitely right.

140
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,770
You have to pretend.

141
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,180
And you?

142
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,410
Ask more questions.

143
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:05,820
Write more,

144
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:07,160
talk less.

145
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:08,560
Okay.

146
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:09,970
For the case,

147
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:11,300
it's a must.

148
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,520
Students,

149
00:06:14,160 --> 00:06:14,880
let me ask you,

150
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:15,940
do you know Lu Yang?

151
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:16,680
No.

152
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,400
Here's the thing.

153
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:18,660
I'm Lu Yang's brother.

154
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,160
I haven't been able to reach him lately.

155
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,890
Do you know where I can find him?

156
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:25,260
I heard from a classmate that he went abroad.

157
00:06:27,320 --> 00:06:29,780
Do you have his contact info? A phone number?

158
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:30,720
No.

159
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,880
None of you do, right?

160
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,200
Yeah.

161
00:06:32,200 --> 00:06:33,320
Okay, thanks.

162
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:34,760
I won't keep you from your class.

163
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:35,000
Okay.

164
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:35,680
Thanks.

165
00:06:40,880 --> 00:06:41,520
Comrades.

166
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:44,320
You won't believe it even if I tell you.

167
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:47,320
Some of his classmates actually believed I was his brother.

168
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:47,920
Alright.

169
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:49,500
Be serious.

170
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:50,680
Let's talk business.

171
00:06:50,680 --> 00:06:52,360
According to Lu Yang's classmates,

172
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,720
something is up with him lately.

173
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,960
He suddenly became very rich

174
00:06:54,960 --> 00:06:56,800
and often hangs out at nightclubs.

175
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:59,000
He also has a girlfriend named Huang Xiaoyun.

176
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:01,000
And both of them are from the countryside.

177
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,120
Huang Xiaoyun.

178
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:03,440
Go on.

179
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,320
Lu Yang courted Huang Xiaoyun

180
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,440
for a very long time.

181
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,520
But Huang Xiaoyun

182
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,280
is quite traditional and hard to get.

183
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:11,000
So he made a bet with his classmates

184
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,600
that he could definitely win her over.

185
00:07:12,600 --> 00:07:13,320
After they

186
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:15,520
officially became boyfriend and girlfriend,

187
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,720
Lu Yang repeatedly demanded

188
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,400
to sleep with her.

189
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:20,560
But she rejected him every time.

190
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:22,280
Between Lu Yang and Tian Liang,

191
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:24,140
there are really countless ties.

192
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:26,240
Lu Yang is Huang Xiaoyun's boyfriend.

193
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,570
Huang Xiaoyun lives at Ye Qiming's house.

194
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,200
Ye Qiming and Xia Lin are married.

195
00:07:30,200 --> 00:07:32,200
Xia Lin and Tian Liang are involved.

196
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,000
It comes full circle.

197
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:34,840
Look.

198
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,880
This is what I collected,

199
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:38,320
Tian Liang's membership list.

200
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,520
There are 20 people in total.

201
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:41,760
Those who have the means to keep Tian Liang...

202
00:07:41,760 --> 00:07:42,440
Only six,

203
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:44,320
but none of them had the time to commit the crime.

204
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,520
And some of them

205
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:48,280
weren't even in Tongjiang City when the crime happened.

206
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,480
This means one thing.

207
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:52,210
We're looking in the wrong direction.

208
00:07:52,320 --> 00:07:53,440
We need to change our approach.

209
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:54,640
Change our approach.

210
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:58,130
Let's go.

211
00:07:58,840 --> 00:08:00,840
Zhao, help me put this in the locker.

212
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:22,940
Nice environment.

213
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:23,560
What?

214
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,000
I mean here.

215
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:27,820
The environment is nice. It shouldn't be cheap.

216
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:28,810
Look over there.

217
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,260
The booth on the right.

218
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:30,920
That girl.

219
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,960
Every time Lu Yang comes, he stays with her.

220
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:35,200
There are three girls over there. Which one?

221
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,000
Don't point.

222
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:42,360
Are you kidding me?

223
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,060
Do I look like I'm kidding?

224
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:46,780
Come on.

225
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,760
For work.

226
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,080
For the case.

227
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,240
Okay, I'll go.

228
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,140
Hey, handsome.

229
00:08:56,240 --> 00:08:57,040
Are you alone?

230
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:00,680
Come over there and hang out with me.

231
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,160
Okay.

232
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,760
Let's just have a few drinks here.

233
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,320
My treat.

234
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:12,160
Okay.

235
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:14,640
Order whatever you want to drink.

236
00:09:14,640 --> 00:09:15,640
It's on me.

237
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,440
Just pour two glasses of wine.

238
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,900
Is it your first time here?

239
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:22,260
I don't usually come here.

240
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,720
Have some drinks and relax.

241
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:29,720
Do you work here?

242
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:30,760
Yes.

243
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:33,500
Come on.

244
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:39,780
What should I call you?

245
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,640
Just call me Xiaoju.

246
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:44,800
I'll look for you when I come here in the future.

247
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:45,760
No problem.

248
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:47,100
Next time you come,

249
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:49,040
just tell the guard you're looking for Xiaoju,

250
00:09:49,040 --> 00:09:50,560
and he will bring you to me.

251
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:56,780
What do you think of me?

252
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:00,400
Are you single?

253
00:10:03,400 --> 00:10:04,760
You must not be single.

254
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,880
Let me ask you something.

255
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:07,920
Tell me.

256
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:11,300
Have you seen this person?

257
00:10:16,920 --> 00:10:17,480
Police.

258
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:20,740
Answer him.

259
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,660
Are you familiar with him?

260
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:24,480
Not familiar.

261
00:10:25,160 --> 00:10:26,320
He doesn't come often.

262
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,560
In the past month,

263
00:10:27,760 --> 00:10:29,000
he came quite frequently,

264
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:31,240
and ordered several bottles of good wine each time.

265
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:32,100
Tell the truth.

266
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:39,450
Has this person been here with him?

267
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:41,500
Never seen him.

268
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,040
He always comes alone.

269
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,160
Hello.

270
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:50,240
Hello.

271
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:28,020
Do you know why we are looking for you?

272
00:11:29,040 --> 00:11:29,770
I don't know.

273
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,200
When was the last time

274
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,260
you saw Tian Liang?

275
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:34,360
Tian Liang?

276
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,370
I don't know him.

277
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:40,080
We came to you after watching the surveillance video

278
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,680
of you following Tian Liang.

279
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:43,620
I... I just followed him for a bit.

280
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,460
Then I found it boring,

281
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,120
so I left.

282
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:49,220
If you don't know him, why did you follow him?

283
00:11:50,360 --> 00:11:51,760
You might be the last person

284
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:52,820
who saw Tian Liang.

285
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,850
So you'd better tell the truth.

286
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:57,280
Lu Yang,

287
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:01,010
I wouldn't have come to you if I didn't have evidence.

288
00:12:01,160 --> 00:12:01,760
By the way,

289
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,560
is this button yours?

290
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:09,240
No.

291
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:11,090
Absolutely not.

292
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,570
Look at that piece of clothing.

293
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:17,120
How did it end up here?

294
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,330
I don't even know when I lost it.

295
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:24,760
That night,

296
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:27,440
you saw Tian Liang staggering out of the bar.

297
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:29,600
Without thinking much,

298
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:30,530
you followed him

299
00:12:31,200 --> 00:12:34,000
all the way to the corner of the convenience store.

300
00:12:45,880 --> 00:12:47,410
Then, seeing no one around,

301
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:49,800
you went straight up and knocked him down.

302
00:12:49,800 --> 00:12:51,000
You grabbed Tian Liang by the collar

303
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:53,530
and punched him in the face one after another.

304
00:12:53,800 --> 00:12:55,880
He was drunk and completely unable to fight back,

305
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:58,080
lying there at the mercy of your punches and kicks.

306
00:12:58,080 --> 00:13:00,080
In a panic, he tore off your button.

307
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:01,600
Scum.

308
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:03,400
Is that so?

309
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:05,440
Pretty much.

310
00:13:06,840 --> 00:13:08,170
Then he probably did it.

311
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,840
I didn't kill Tian Liang.

312
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,920
Did I say Tian Liang was dead?

313
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:17,800
Lu Yang.

314
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,440
Speaking now will save you.

315
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:27,480
Xia Lin.

316
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:29,880
I'll send you the photos from our trip

317
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:30,560
later.

318
00:13:31,320 --> 00:13:33,120
Did you take good pictures of me?

319
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,360
Of course.

320
00:13:39,680 --> 00:13:40,240
Lu Yang,

321
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,520
what's wrong?

322
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:43,170
Nothing.

323
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:45,040
I'll call you back later.

324
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:51,000
Come in.

325
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:57,280
Lu Yang.

326
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,250
Why are you here?

327
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:03,720
Nothing much.

328
00:14:06,920 --> 00:14:08,520
If you have something to say,

329
00:14:08,560 --> 00:14:09,320
just say it.

330
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,520
How much do you think it's worth?

331
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:30,120
How did you know you could get money for that photo?

332
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:31,180
I know her husband.

333
00:14:31,560 --> 00:14:32,420
He is very rich.

334
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:33,920
Not that guy.

335
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,840
My girlfriend lives at their house.

336
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,320
What is your girlfriend's name?

337
00:14:37,320 --> 00:14:38,180
Huang Xiaoyun.

338
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:43,330
How much money did Xia Lin give you?

339
00:14:45,560 --> 00:14:46,820
She just kicked me out.

340
00:14:47,400 --> 00:14:49,530
You mean she didn't give you any money?

341
00:14:49,640 --> 00:14:51,640
How else could I have followed Tian Liang?

342
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:53,440
I wanted to take some pictures of them

343
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,600
to blackmail them for money.

344
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:55,840
Are you sure the last time

345
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:57,970
you saw Tian Liang, he was still alive?

346
00:14:58,040 --> 00:14:58,760
I'm sure.

347
00:14:59,920 --> 00:15:01,960
He even stood up and looked around for someone.

348
00:15:01,960 --> 00:15:04,000
So you didn't see him again after that?

349
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:04,600
No.

350
00:15:04,760 --> 00:15:06,360
I went to an internet cafe afterwards.

351
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,820
They should have a record.

352
00:15:07,880 --> 00:15:09,960
We've seen the security footage from the internet cafe.

353
00:15:09,960 --> 00:15:12,160
But you only stayed there for two hours.

354
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,280
What happened next?

355
00:15:13,280 --> 00:15:14,680
Then I came back to sleep.

356
00:15:15,120 --> 00:15:16,250
Can anyone prove it?

357
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:19,120
I live alone.

358
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:22,320
But there are a few neighbors on the street.

359
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,520
They might remember.

360
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:27,530
Alright.

361
00:15:27,680 --> 00:15:28,540
Let's split up.

362
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:29,680
You go find...

363
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,560
Never mind. I'll go find Xia Lin.

364
00:15:32,720 --> 00:15:33,200
Okay.

365
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:36,320
Then I'll take Xiao Li to find Huang Xiaoyun.

366
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:36,760
Let's go.
